<br>
Anyone else wanting to come, your welcome to sign up. However, I won't go past 5 full groups. Those that signed up first, get first consideration. But sometimes people have things come up, and cancle, so please, if your still interested, sign up and I will let you know.<br>
<br>
Please remember, Magic and Fire resists are important in the final fight with Naggy. We will also be clearing the fire giants ourselves, but that will only take an hour to do.<br>
<br>
Since I know classes and levels before hand, I can start making the groups up now. It's important to be on time. Druids can port you righ to the meeting spot in Lavastorm, Try and be there between 1:30 and 2 pm eastern time as we want to move in no later then 2:15 eastern time. (that's 1:15 central, 12:15 mountain, 11:15 pacific time).<br>
<br>
The basic statragy is this:<br>
<br>
1. Form Groups.<br>
<br>
2. Groups move into Nagafen's Lair one at a time. Eveyone gets shrunk, save the Main Tank, the archers and the Enchanters (so everyone can see the MT cleary, so archers and enchanters can see over everyones heads). Groups can buff up.<br>
<br>
3. Two groups will clear kobolds on the way to the Fire giants. This is so that we don't get all clustered together ontop of each other. <br>
<br>
4. Kill Fire Giants.<br>
<br>
5. Kill Lord Nagafen<br>
<br>
6. Get Drunk.<br>
<br>
Further details will be, of course, explained once there and inside.<br>
<br>
I look forward to seeing you all Saturday, if I don't get a chance to say hello in game before hand.<br>
<br>
Stavenham Valiant. <br>
